data.description: Immaculate, like new construction home in the desirable Larkin neighborhood. This impressive home is packed full of upgrades! You will enjoy the spacious open floorplan where the enormous kitchen opens to the family room and breakfast area. You will appreciate the elegant formal dining room when entertaining family and friends. Connected to the amazing kitchen is a perfectly sized butler's pantry and walk in pantry. You will delight in the crisp clean design of this home. The primary bedroom features an additional space for your enjoyment as an exercise room, sitting/reading space, office, nursery, or any other purpose suited to you! Just off the family room you will love the sunroom which creates an immediate feeling of relaxation. Larkin features the newly renovated 500 club golf course. The community will also offer pickle ball and bocce ball. Also available is a community swimming pool, tennis courts, playground, picnic area, and sidewalks with street lights!
